<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="publishing-dita-documents" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Publishing DITA Documents</title>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <p id="note-about-java">DITA documents are published with DITA Open Toolkit V1.4 that requires installation of Java not older than J2SE v 1.4.2_08. For instructions, see <xref href="installing-java-on-windows.xml"/> and <xref href="installing-java-on-linux.xml"/>.</p>
      <p id="publish-dita-document-intro">DITA documents can be published to HTML and PDF format. Publishing to PDF can be done with FOP out-of-the-box.</p>
      <p>To publish a document, do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step id="step-call-publish-dialog">
        <cmd>Call up the <keyword>Publish Dialog</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>In Serna, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Publish</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Specify the output format.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>In the <uicontrol>Publish Dialog</uicontrol>, select the publishing output from the <uicontrol>Publishing output</uicontrol> drop-down list.</p>
        </info>
        <choices>
          <choice>
            <p>To publish HTML, select <uicontrol>HTML</uicontrol>. </p>
          </choice>
          <choice>
            <p>To publish PDF with FOP, select <uicontrol>PDF</uicontrol>.</p>
          </choice>
        </choices>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Specify the output filename and location.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>In the <uicontrol>Write to</uicontrol> field, you can specify the output filename. You can use the <uicontrol>Browse</uicontrol> button to specify the output file location.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step id="click-generate">
        <cmd>Publish the document.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>Click the <uicontrol>Generate</uicontrol> button.</p>
          <image href="publish-dialog-dita-pdf-with-ah.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step id="click-view">
        <cmd>View the published document.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>When the script ends, click the <uicontrol>View</uicontrol> button to view the published document.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
